title: Everybody *Screws* With Biden with Jack Posobiec and Ken Paxton
itunes:title: Everybody *Screws* With Biden with Jack Posobiec and Ken Paxton
description:
With Charlie out on assignment, friend of the show and Host of TPUSA’s Human Events Daily, Jack Posobiec steps in to talk about Biden’s hot mic moment yesterday, and prove all the ways that everyone, including the CCP, F*$!s with Biden, especially OPEC. Next, Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton joins to talk about his latest win in the battle against DACA. He explains what it means for Texas and the massive implication it has for Biden’s nearly 5 million illegal border crossers in just his first two years in office.
